column2: "The threads of fate that stretched from the past have been severed. Apparitions such as us are no longer needed."
"There's no need to be sad. In escaping this cycle of rebirth, you have saved me too."
"Matoi. Live your life as you see fit."
"Beyond lies a future not even the all-knowing can record."
"A future that cannot be written. One that only you can experience."
"...However. There is one thing I can say for certain."
"The future that awaits will surely be worth living for."
"This is... the Mothership? ...Was that a dream?"
